SubjectLoran-C Station, Williams Lake B.C. 1991 Termination of Treaty (US) #12
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America constituting an Agreement amending the Agreement of June 3, 1976, relating to the Construction, Operation and Maintenance of a Loran-C Station in the vicinity of Williams Lake, B.C., done on 3 and 8 May 1991.
